{"title":"木马推荐书","authors":["刘征　苗地"],"dates":[{"year":1987,"month":1,"day":6}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"木马推荐书"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刘　征诗　苗　地画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"踏破铁鞋寻觅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪有马能千里？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工夫不负苦心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"而今找到一匹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一是为人老实，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"决不咬啃跑踢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二是作风正派，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总是眼顺眉低；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三是步伐稳健，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最讲安全第一；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四是使用顺手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由你推来拉去。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阅尽腾骧万马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唯它可靠无比。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"理应破格提拔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"推上领导岗位。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}